|GKB-- Twin Sky Blades -------------------------------------------|000

Current: |CKBTekali|000
Command: |CKBtwinskyblades <type>|000
Aliases: |CKBtwinskyblade|000, |CKBtwinsky|000
Guild Level: 10

Twin Sky Blades shapes two Sky Blades at once.  It costs the same
Tekali nwyfre as invoking Sky Blade twice one at a time, but saves you
from waiting through the cooldown between the two invocations.

The available blade types follow your normal Sky Blade training and
alignment restrictions.  If you already have any Sky Blades, release
them before invoking the twin form.
